<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個月也過了一半，<delay20 />
終於開始有<delay8 />聖誕節的氣氛啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多該認真地<delay20 />
思考該送什麼禮物了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />如果你有送禮的對象，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />記得別忘了包裝禮物喔。<delay40 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是禮物沒包裝，<delay8 />那可就太破壞氣氛了。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我小時候<delay8 />非常期待能收到禮物，<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我在聖誕節早上<delay20 />
會起得比任何人都還要早<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一生都忘不了那種興奮的感覺咧。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而現在輪到我送人禮物，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種立場<delay8 />
其實也挺令人興奮的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在廣場上<delay8 />擺了一顆非常大的樹～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來這座島<delay8 />也充滿了聖誕節的氣氛喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也趁現在<delay8 />趕快拍幾張照片吧，<delay40 />
雖然這種事都是老了才會想做，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過留下回憶<delay8 />可是很重要的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>